### Welcome to the Johns Hopkins Developer Community
The Technology Innovation Center is sponsoring a new Hopkins Developer Community, aiming to bring together developers to share their knowledge, skills, experience, tools and resources.  

#### Goals
- Identify the community of developers
- Share best practices
- SDLC
- DevOps
- Documentation
- Tools and processes
- Technologies

What’s here already?
What’s coming next?

#### First Meeting
The first meeting will be October 16 from 1 to 3pm. We will follow-up with location details in early October.
